Build a generic agent-material batch from agent-produced strategy packages

Usage: ict-engine auto-quant-agent-material-batch [OPTIONS] --symbol <SYMBOL>

Options:
      --symbol <SYMBOL>
          Instrument identifier supplied by the caller
      --material <MATERIALS>
          Repeatable path to an agent-produced strategy material package (.json)
      --max-parallel <MAX_PARALLEL>
          Maximum number of independent jobs to dispatch in parallel [default: 4]
      --state-dir <STATE_DIR>
          State directory holding the generic agent-material batch artifact [env: ICT_ENGINE_STATE_DIR=] [default: state]
      --repo-url <REPO_URL>
          Optional Auto-Quant repo URL or local path override used when bootstrapping the shared workspace
      --tracked-branch <TRACKED_BRANCH>
          Optional Auto-Quant branch override used when bootstrapping the shared workspace
  -h, --help
          Print help
